<P>AN HISTORY OF THE EARTH, AND ANIMATED NATURE:</P>
<P>BY OLIVER GOLDSMITH.</P>
<P>IN EIGHT VOLUMES.</P>
<P>VOL. I.</P>
<P><HI>LONDON:</HI> Printed for J. NOURSE, in the STRAND, BOOKSELLER
